{"tid":1000851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日晏就眼訓","createTime":"2019-01-29T16:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T17:00:39.000Z","uid":127073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b17071e77847bc8eb3007491ea8fda2d0e9e603","tid":1000851,"uid":127073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"讀緊書 成日夜晚訓唔到<br />\n朝早9點堂成日起唔到身<br />\n起到身又好眼訓<br />\n一到放學番屋企就忍唔住訓番個零鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果到夜晚又好精神<br />\n<br />\n上兩點堂 11點起身<br />\n岩岩起個下好精神<br />\n食完野番到學校已經好眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無過來人教下我<br />\n<br />\n（利伸：只係番學先係咁 番工好正常 ）"},{"pid":"3bb0e151de78181bf4dd3226b804dd6bb899d3eb","tid":1000851,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"9點鐘訓左而家醒左<br />\n聽朝仲要返早<br />\n即係聽朝返工又準備眼訓<br />\n唉唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}